      answer: 1,
      why: "Best practice is exactly the opposite of decentralization: a centralized group treasury with frequent (monthly) senior management and risk-personnel oversight. The other distractors invert real findings from the reading — decentralization was identified as a major SOURCE of failure, and both compensation and contingent/derivative exposures are specifically called out as needing to be INTEGRATED into (not separated from) the LTP process."
